#. </h5><p><a class="sc" id="33"></a><a class="pts-cs-empty" id="bu-ss.8.3"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-ss.8.3.1"></a><a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.283"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1588"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:37.4"
msgid "Adiṭṭhassa hoti pārājikaṃ dhammaṃ ajjhāpajjanto."
msgstr "Although he has not seen it, he accuses someone of having committed an offense entailing expulsion:"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:37.5"
msgid "Tañce codeti—“diṭṭho mayā, pārājikaṃ dhammaṃ ajjhāpannosi, assamaṇosi, asakya­putti­yosi, natthi tayā saddhiṃ uposatho vā pavāraṇā vā saṃghakammaṃ vā”ti, āpatti vācāya, vācāya saṃ­ghā­di­sesassa."
msgstr "“I’ve seen that you’ve committed an offense entailing expulsion."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:37.6"
msgid "assamaṇosi, asakya­putti­yosi,"
msgstr "You’re no longer an ascetic, not a son of the Sakyan;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:37.7"
msgid "natthi tayā saddhiṃ uposatho vā pavāraṇā vā saṃghakammaṃ vā”ti,"
msgstr "you’re excluded from the observance-day ceremony, from the invitation ceremony, and from the formal procedures of the Order.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:37.8"
msgid "āpatti vācāya, vācāya saṃ­ghā­di­sesassa."
msgstr "For each statement, he commits an offense entailing suspension."

