msgid "Tañce suddhadiṭṭhi samāno anokāsaṃ kārāpetvā cāvanādhippāyo vadeti, āpatti saṃghādisesena dukkaṭassa."
msgstr "If one thinks he is pure, but then, without having obtained his consent, speaks with the aim of making him leave the monastic life, one commits one offense entailing suspension and one offense of wrong conduct."

